ActSpecies at Risk Act
SubjectExemption Order for Certain Licences, Authorizations and Documents (Bull Trout (Saskatchewan-Nelson Rivers Populations))
PrecisEXEMPTION ORDER FOR CERTAIN LICENCES, AUTHORIZATIONS AND DOCUMENTS (BULL TROUT (SASKATCHEWAN-NELSON RIVERS POPULATIONS)) in order to allow for the continuation of certain recreational and indigenous fisheries while the recovery strategies are being developed which may allow for inclusions of exemptions for these activities on an ongoing basis, conditional on meeting conservation objectives.
